es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唱城邦歌串陳雲都叫港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"明明陳雲都入到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"永續都係港獨?"},{"pid":"815d41e99fc23fc20ac98de538950e5e5662f61f","tid":595722,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794fec5feef43022a7b19e94ce872eba0d353ef0","tid":595722,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815d41e99fc23fc20ac98de538950e5e5662f61f","tid":595722,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"京官不滿但應該都無後續<br />\n下次選舉就難講"},{"pid":"10c9bb0687dc10bdf43238a06f25505b5b70f342","tid":595722,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5562218eaff61b6a5e7051369675dd8563ec2bc3","tid":595722,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77e613bd6fca75cf0363e265583b0545625554c9","tid":595722,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"支那人咁玻璃心 真係麻撚煩"}]}